has  been  brought  about  because  of  a  failure  somewhere.  The  only 
thing that is—that we can say is that the hearing is part of exam-
ination  and  accountability  that  can  help  us  find  where  the  prob-
lems exist within our jurisdictional areas of responsibility, and how 
they can be addressed. 

