shaking when I walked out of his office. It was horrible. And I have 
to  say,  I’ve  been  yelled  at  by  the  best  of  them.  You  know,  I  have 
appeared  in  Federal  court  before  judges  who,  lawyers  like  to  com-
monly say, think they’re the closest thing next to God, maybe other 
than Congresspeople. 

