to  notify  the  Department  of  Justice,  the  Attorney  General.  So, 
when  allegations  came  in,  we  immediately  started  working  with 
them and in joint cases with the FBI. And so, our cases took a little 
different—our reports took a little different road. So, anything that 
did  come  through,  you  know,  the—it  was  very  difficult  to  get  the 
report out in any possible timeframe. 

Representative MILLER. Ms. Herzog? 
