judgment? 

Ms. BRIAN. I don’t think there’s any question that it does. 
Representative MILLER. Dr. Light? 
Dr.  LIGHT.  Same.  Same  answer.  It  is  an  impairment,  and  it  vio-

Representative  MILLER.  The  standards  of  professional  con-

lates those standards. 

duct—— 

Dr. LIGHT. Right. 
Representative MILLER. And these are issued by the PCIE which 
