EXCERPTS FROM RECORD OF INVESTIGATION OF HON.  ROBERT W.  COBB,  OFFICE OF 
INSPECTOR GENERAL,  NASA,  AUGUST 30,  2006  (PAGES 49–54,  59,  140–142,195– 
