often he held ‘‘Director’s luncheons’’ with COBB. O’Keefe stated, ‘‘I’m not sure. Once 
or  twice  a  month  I  suppose,  or  more  often.’’  O’Keefe  stated  others  often  present  at 
the 
included:  Fred  Gregory,  Deputy  Administrator,  NASA;  John 
